title: Ep - 135 - JENNIE MARIE FROM MAMA MEDIUM ON TLC / BEN MANDELKER FROM WATCH WHAT CRAPPENS
description:
Jennie Marie from TLC’s new series Mama Medium is gifted with the extraordinary ability to talk to the dead. Not only is Jennie Marie a medium, psychic, and fourth generation clairvoyant, but she also has an uncanny gift of connecting with people who are otherwise incapable of communicating for themselves. She discusses the afterlife, tapping into spirits, and why she had to quit her job as a real estate agent because she kept seeing dead people. 


Ben Mandelker from Watch What Crappens podcast reviews the season premiere of Real Housewives of New Jersey. 


Mary Payne Gilbert from Payne in the Pod podcast reviews Bravo’s new show Get a Room with Carson and Thom, featuring Carson Kressley and Thom Filicia redecorating homes in America. 


Reality Life with Kate Casey
